to maintain law and order.

1034
01:13:31.381 --> 01:13:35.930
Now, either Crane didn't
understand that, or didn't care.

1035
01:13:36.015 --> 01:13:39.904
And now look at the mess
he's making me clean up.

1036
01:13:39.988 --> 01:13:44.220
What's worse is, he's infected
someone... dear to me.

1037
01:13:44.305 --> 01:13:45.390
Block.

1038
01:13:45.475 --> 01:13:47.814
Been a good friend, family,

1039
01:13:47.895 --> 01:13:49.984
for as long as I can remember.

1040
01:13:50.068 --> 01:13:52.774
Sir, I may be
out of line here, but...

1041
01:13:55.112 --> 01:13:57.081
would you like us
to have a word with him?

1042
01:13:58.814 --> 01:14:01.859
Someone in the FBI created
a false criminal record

1043
01:14:01.944 --> 01:14:05.197
for a Federal agent involved in
a secret FBI program.

1044
01:14:05.279 --> 01:14:08.095
That fake record was then sent
out on the police wire

1045
01:14:08.176 --> 01:14:10.729
so that the media
would ignore him.

1046
01:14:10.813 --> 01:14:12.411
Drew obviously didn't.

1047
01:14:12.493 --> 01:14:15.260
And now that agent
and Drew are both dead.

1048
01:14:15.341 --> 01:14:16.832
Interesting.

1049
01:14:18.335 --> 01:14:20.064
Almost.

1050
01:14:20.145 --> 01:14:22.770
We run that, and tomorrow we get
a simple, logical explanation.

1051
01:14:22.854 --> 01:14:24.153
We have no proof to refute it.

1052
01:14:24.234 --> 01:14:26.714
Or corrupt FBI agents
following us home.

1053
01:14:26.797 --> 01:14:28.023
- And then there's that.
- Fine.

1054
01:14:28.104 --> 01:14:29.957
You want more proof,
I'll just call the FBI

1055
01:14:30.042 --> 01:14:31.917
and ask for an interview with
the asshole that killed Dusty.

1056
01:14:32.002 --> 01:14:33.895
Mira, I know this is
frustrating,

1057
01:14:33.979 --> 01:14:35.854
but what we need is
an actual living person

1058
01:14:35.939 --> 01:14:37.435
who can help tell the story.

1059
01:14:37.520 --> 01:14:40.430
Someone with specifics who can
help fill in the basics.

1060
01:14:40.515 --> 01:14:44.287
The who, the what, the when.
And if we're lucky, the why.

1061
01:14:44.372 --> 01:14:45.877
The why is obvious.

1062
01:14:45.961 --> 01:14:48.180
Obvious to you
isn't good enough.

1063
01:14:48.261 --> 01:14:50.908
Listen, if we are dealing
with a corrupt head of the FBI,

1064
01:14:50.992 --> 01:14:52.911
they will cover up the cover up
with another cover up

1065
01:14:52.993 --> 01:14:54.444
and they'll spin it as
some top secret

1066
01:14:54.529 --> 01:14:56.045
national security operation
that hides

1067
01:14:56.127 --> 01:14:58.051
behind the veil of need-to-know.

1068
01:14:58.136 --> 01:15:01.747
The American people
need to know the truth.

1069
01:15:01.832 --> 01:15:03.452
That's what
I used to think.

1070
01:15:03.533 --> 01:15:05.189
And you don't anymore?

1071
01:15:05.273 --> 01:15:08.033
Honestly, undecided.

1072
01:15:08.117 --> 01:15:10.027
Sometimes I think
it's better to live

1073
01:15:10.109 --> 01:15:12.087
in the happiness of the unknown.

1074
01:15:13.488 --> 01:15:15.033
The United States government is

1075
01:15:15.118 --> 01:15:17.261
murdering its own
innocent citizens.

1076
01:15:20.831 --> 01:15:21.966
Yeah.

1077
01:15:23.500 --> 01:15:24.835
That is messed up.

1078
01:15:26.002 --> 01:15:28.372
We need to nail these assholes.

1079
01:15:28.456 --> 01:15:30.091
Nothing? Nothing?

1080
01:15:30.175 --> 01:15:32.310
No forwarding address?
No phone records?

1081
01:15:32.395 --> 01:15:33.823
Would you be able to pull

1082
01:15:33.908 --> 01:15:35.948
school enrollment records
for Natalie Block?

1083
01:15:36.029 --> 01:15:37.524
Check the entire country.

1084
01:15:37.608 --> 01:15:39.194
Actually, Sam, one more thing.

1085
01:15:39.278 --> 01:15:40.948
Search all informants
who recently entered.

1086
01:15:41.033 --> 01:15:42.234
Witness Protection.

1087
01:15:42.319 --> 01:15:43.765
They may have changed
their last names,

1088
01:15:43.849 --> 01:15:45.389
but they would have kept
their first.

1089
01:15:45.470 --> 01:15:47.332
Amanda and Natalie.

1090
01:15:47.417 --> 01:15:49.301
Okay. Hey... hey, Sam.

1091
01:15:49.386 --> 01:15:51.005
Let's keep this between us.

1092
01:15:51.087 --> 01:15:53.460
Do this for me,
consider us even.

1093
01:15:53.542 --> 01:15:54.529
Thanks, Sam.

1094
01:16:01.438 --> 01:16:03.393
Block.

1095
01:16:03.475 --> 01:16:05.555
Oh, yeah, uh, Mira.

1096
01:16:05.640 --> 01:16:08.779
Listen, uh, now's not
a good time.

1097
01:16:12.046 --> 01:16:13.895
What do you have?

1098
01:16:13.979 --> 01:16:15.399
Robinson's very capable

1099
01:16:15.483 --> 01:16:18.131
when it comes
to cleaning up his messes.

1100
01:16:18.215 --> 01:16:20.895
I would say this has his
fingerprints all over it.

1101
01:16:20.979 --> 01:16:24.337
I need a quote
from a reliable source.

1102
01:16:24.420 --> 01:16:26.963
I'm the last person
you want as a source.

1103
01:16:27.047 --> 01:16:28.247
But you know it's wrong.

1104
01:16:28.328 --> 01:16:30.875
I know what I know,
but my hands are dirty.

1105
01:16:30.957 --> 01:16:33.337
You put my name out there,
my credibility,

1106
01:16:33.421 --> 01:16:35.140
it'll come into question.

1107
01:16:35.224 --> 01:16:36.292
Even my sanity.

1108
01:16:36.375 --> 01:16:38.147
They'll say I made the
whole thing up,

1109
01:16:38.230 --> 01:16:41.416
all in the name of
protecting myself.

1110
01:16:41.497 --> 01:16:44.359
Probably wind up like Dusty.

1111
01:16:44.443 --> 01:16:46.024
I still don't understand
why Robinson

1112
01:16:46.109 --> 01:16:47.951
would go to all these lengths.

1113
01:16:48.984 --> 01:16:52.858
Same reason Hoover did it
for almost 50 years.

1114
01:16:52.939 --> 01:16:55.272
To maintain power, control,

1115
01:16:55.356 --> 01:16:58.372
which will give him a
shelf life that'll outlast

1116
01:16:58.453 --> 01:17:02.136
every politician on Capitol Hill
and in the White House.

1117
01:17:02.219 --> 01:17:04.313
You can't let them
get away with this.

1118
01:17:04.395 --> 01:17:07.310
I mean, this is your chance
to right all your wrongs.

1119
01:17:07.394 --> 01:17:10.011
What's done is done.
There's no going backwards.

1120
01:17:10.095 --> 01:17:12.046
Then let's go forward
and prevent Robinson

1121
01:17:12.131 --> 01:17:14.546
from abusing his power
in the future.

1122
01:17:14.631 --> 01:17:15.992
If we don't stand up to him,

1123
01:17:16.073 --> 01:17:17.979
he'll just keep growing
Operation Unity.

1124
01:17:18.979 --> 01:17:20.234
He probably will.

1125
01:17:20.319 --> 01:17:23.926
Remember, it's your job
to protect the agents.

1126
01:17:24.010 --> 01:17:25.462
How many more Dusty's
have to die for you

1127
01:17:25.546 --> 01:17:26.720
to stop looking the other way?

1128
01:17:31.929 --> 01:17:33.439
As long as I've worked
for Robinson,

1129
01:17:33.524 --> 01:17:37.064
I've... I've never heard
of Operation Unity.

1130
01:17:37.149 --> 01:17:38.353
Somebody must know.

1131
01:17:38.435 --> 01:17:40.444
These sort of people
don't talk out of turn.

1132
01:17:40.529 --> 01:17:43.407
Maybe, but secrets
this big can't hide forever.

1133
01:17:47.010 --> 01:17:49.220
Robinson has a safe in his house

1134
01:17:49.305 --> 01:17:51.654
where he keeps a
record of everyone

1135
01:17:51.738 --> 01:17:54.122
and everything
the Bureau touches.

1136
01:17:54.206 --> 01:17:56.926
- Everything?
- Everything.

1137
01:17:57.011 --> 01:17:59.372
It's his security blanket,

1138
01:17:59.456 --> 01:18:03.569
ammunition in case anyone
decides to turn against him.

1139
01:18:03.653 --> 01:18:10.033
If there's a paper trail on
Operation Unity, it's in there.

1140
01:20:08.283 --> 01:20:10.493
What do you mean,
he blew up your car?

1141
01:20:10.578 --> 01:20:12.792
Block shot it
with a grenade launcher.

1142
01:20:17.828 --> 01:20:19.764
I must never
underestimate that man.

1143
01:20:22.466 --> 01:20:25.229
Where is the crazy
son-of-a-bitch now?

1144
01:20:25.313 --> 01:20:26.636
Don't know.

1145
01:20:27.636 --> 01:20:29.511
Well, I do.

1146
01:20:29.595 --> 01:20:30.662
He's here.

1147
01:20:30.746 --> 01:20:34.255
- Here as in?
- As in, my front door.

1148
01:20:34.337 --> 01:20:37.514
If you're not too busy,
you might wanna stop by.

1149
01:20:45.453 --> 01:20:47.189
Wasn't expecting you.

1150
01:20:48.492 --> 01:20:50.158
Got a minute?

1151
01:20:56.363 --> 01:20:59.112
- You sent them. Right.
- I sent who?

1152
01:20:59.194 --> 01:21:01.274
You know, if you were
just honest with me,

1153
01:21:01.359 --> 01:21:02.818
I'd have more respect for you.

1154
01:21:02.899 --> 01:21:05.211
I take it this isn't
a friendly pop in.

1155
01:21:05.295 --> 01:21:06.453
What the hell do you want?

1156
01:21:06.537 --> 01:21:08.819
All your files
on Operation Unity.

1157
01:21:08.903 --> 01:21:10.546
I'm afraid that's not happening.

1158
01:21:11.716 --> 01:21:13.483
It's not a request, Gabriel.

1159
01:21:15.185 --> 01:21:16.796
This is a huge mistake.

1160
01:21:16.881 --> 01:21:18.817
I'll add it to my list.
Open it.

1161
01:21:18.899 --> 01:21:20.412
Or what?

1162
01:21:20.497 --> 01:21:22.626
Are you really gonna
shoot me, Travis?

1163
01:21:23.627 --> 01:21:25.162
Yes, I will.

1164
01:21:30.902 --> 01:21:32.283
The hard drive.

1165
01:21:32.367 --> 01:21:34.167
I need to see what's on it.

1166
01:21:34.252 --> 01:21:35.706
Load it up.

1167
01:21:43.645 --> 01:21:45.314
Step aside.

1168
01:21:50.487 --> 01:21:53.157
The world isn't ready
to see what's on that drive.

1169
01:21:53.238 --> 01:21:55.368
The truth can be difficult,

1170
01:21:55.453 --> 01:21:57.461
but it's better than
the alternative.

1171
01:22:11.408 --> 01:22:12.944
You two, take the back.

1172
01:24:11.060 --> 01:24:13.738
I recommend you walk away.

1173
01:24:13.819 --> 01:24:16.010
This is not your fight.

1174
01:24:16.094 --> 01:24:18.399
You were just taking orders.

1175
01:24:41.993 --> 01:24:44.001
Robinson's using you.

1176
01:24:44.085 --> 01:24:45.828
The way he used me.

1177
01:24:48.064 --> 01:24:50.500
We're just bullets
in his chamber.

1178
01:25:19.462 --> 01:25:20.997
Enough is enough!

1179
01:27:58.956 --> 01:28:00.555
Travis.

1180
01:28:28.283 --> 01:28:30.599
- Who are you?
- Uh...

1181
01:28:30.680 --> 01:28:32.225
This is Pearl.
She works with me.

1182
01:28:32.309 --> 01:28:34.759
Please don't shoot her.

1183
01:28:36.792 --> 01:28:38.622
Can we trust her with this?

1184
01:28:38.703 --> 01:28:40.131
We can.

1185
01:28:45.935 --> 01:28:47.858
Donuts? Really?

1186
01:28:47.939 --> 01:28:49.845
It... it was all I could
find in this dump.

1187
01:28:49.929 --> 01:28:52.011
So, Robinson hid
Amanda and Natalie

1188
01:28:52.095 --> 01:28:54.587
in Witness Protection?

1189
01:28:54.671 --> 01:28:56.613
But no idea where they are?

1190
01:28:57.314 --> 01:28:59.090
Uh-huh, okay.

1191
01:28:59.171 --> 01:29:00.202
Thanks, Sam.

1192
01:29:00.283 --> 01:29:02.551
Yeah. Appreciate you looking.

1193
01:29:09.926 --> 01:29:12.319
Using your family as leverage
against you is so effing wrong.

1194
01:29:12.404 --> 01:29:14.055
Sorry to say.

1195
01:29:14.139 --> 01:29:17.773
Seems relatively minor compared
to everything else he's doing.

1196
01:29:17.854 --> 01:29:21.137
Character assassinations,
political blackmail.

1197
01:29:21.221 --> 01:29:22.787
Looks like flat out murder.

1198
01:29:22.871 --> 01:29:25.948
All under the guise
of protecting democracy.

1199
01:29:26.029 --> 01:29:28.578
What does it say
about Dusty Crane?

1200
01:29:30.881 --> 01:29:32.185
Looks like you've got
everything you'd ever

1201
01:29:32.269 --> 01:29:33.323
want to know about him.

1202
01:29:33.407 --> 01:29:34.916
Oh, there's a video.

1203
01:29:35.000 --> 01:29:36.118
Play it.

1204
01:29:37.252 --> 01:29:39.189
Dustin Crane, Special Agent.

1205
01:29:39.270 --> 01:29:41.341
Your mission?

1206
01:29:41.426 --> 01:29:43.139
You know that.
It's deep infill.

1207
01:29:43.220 --> 01:29:46.368
Have you maintained
contact with the target?

1208
01:29:46.453 --> 01:29:49.336
Yes, the target's name
is Sofia Flores.

1209
01:29:49.420 --> 01:29:51.636
How often
is your exposure?

1210
01:29:51.720 --> 01:29:52.850
Every day,
at least

1211
01:29:52.935 --> 01:29:54.680
a few hours a day,
sometimes longer.

1212
01:29:54.761 --> 01:29:55.988
How have you
been able to maintain that

1213
01:29:56.069 --> 01:29:59.180
level of contact with
an unsuspecting target?

1214
01:29:59.265 --> 01:30:02.179
She, uh, she thinks
I'm her boyfriend.

1215
01:30:03.380 --> 01:30:04.840
And?

1216
01:30:04.921 --> 01:30:06.850
Are you her boyfriend?

1217
01:30:08.152 --> 01:30:10.698
I'd like to think so.

1218
01:30:10.783 --> 01:30:12.854
How long has
this been going on?

1219
01:30:15.725 --> 01:30:18.109
A little over a year now.

1220
01:30:18.192 --> 01:30:20.898
And she has
no idea who you really are?

1221
01:30:22.233 --> 01:30:24.835
No, no. No, she doesn't.

1222
01:30:29.439 --> 01:30:31.711
You can see
it in his face.

1223
01:30:31.795 --> 01:30:33.711
They were in love.

1224
01:30:34.743 --> 01:30:36.645
I feel sick.

1225
01:31:02.206 --> 01:31:05.051
What are you doing?
You're going the wrong way.

1226
01:31:05.134 --> 01:31:09.103
You knew Dusty Crane was
in love with Sofia Flores.

1227
01:31:09.185 --> 01:31:10.072
Travis!

1228
01:31:10.154 --> 01:31:12.157
You got nervous he might
come clean to her.

1229
01:31:12.238 --> 01:31:14.127
The thought that someone
with her influence

1230
01:31:14.210 --> 01:31:16.417
might find out what you were
up to scared you.

1231
01:31:16.501 --> 01:31:18.430
You slippery shit.

1232
01:31:18.515 --> 01:31:19.938
Pull the damn car over.

1233
01:31:20.020 --> 01:31:22.763
That's why you killed her,
and then him.

1234
01:31:22.846 --> 01:31:24.729
To protect your
secret operation.

1235
01:31:24.810 --> 01:31:26.828
You know nothing.

1236
01:31:31.135 --> 01:31:32.087
Listen carefully.

1237
01:31:32.171 --> 01:31:35.242
Operation Unity is going public.
The whole thing.

1238
01:31:35.323 --> 01:31:37.376
- Bullshit.
- You need to listen.

1239
01:31:37.460 --> 01:31:39.076
Not to you, I don't.

1240
01:31:41.877 --> 01:31:43.779
How about now?

1241
01:31:45.479 --> 01:31:47.457
Our arrangement never happened.

1242
01:31:47.542 --> 01:31:49.063
You're going to destroy my file

1243
01:31:49.145 --> 01:31:51.024
and forget everything
I've done for you.

1244
01:31:51.109 --> 01:31:52.832
After that, you will go public

1245
01:31:52.916 --> 01:31:54.462
with the truth
about the operation.

1246
01:31:54.546 --> 01:31:56.270
I am the director of the most

1247
01:31:56.353 --> 01:31:59.435
powerful organization
in the world.

1248
01:31:59.518 --> 01:32:02.304
I will not bargain with you.

1249
01:32:02.386 --> 01:32:04.220
Then call it coercion.

1250
01:32:04.304 --> 01:32:07.304
If I'm not being convincing
enough, there are other ways.

1251
01:32:32.997 --> 01:32:35.837
Fine. We'll do it your way.

1252
01:32:35.921 --> 01:32:37.353
I'll clean your record.

1253
01:32:37.435 --> 01:32:41.078
But there is no chance in hell
I am admitting to anything,

1254
01:32:41.162 --> 01:32:45.313
and if I hear a whisper
of Operation Unity in the press,

1255
01:32:45.395 --> 01:32:48.779
you'll be indicted
before the day is over.

1256
01:32:50.514 --> 01:32:54.988
That was the last threat
you will ever make to me.

1257
01:32:55.073 --> 01:32:57.354
You wanna put a bullet
in your old friend?

1258
01:32:59.390 --> 01:33:01.411
Go ahead.

1259
01:33:01.493 --> 01:33:03.926
You'd be doing me a favor.

1260
01:33:04.895 --> 01:33:06.363
Please, do it.

1261
01:33:08.131 --> 01:33:09.466
Do it!

1262
01:33:14.171 --> 01:33:15.166
No.

1263
01:33:15.250 --> 01:33:16.979
You're not getting
off that easy.

1264
01:33:17.063 --> 01:33:18.921
The truth needs to be told.

1265
01:33:19.005 --> 01:33:21.854
And you're gonna be
the one to tell it.

1266
01:33:21.938 --> 01:33:25.814
But first, you tell me.
Where's my family?

1267
01:33:57.648 --> 01:33:59.216
There she is!

1268
01:33:59.301 --> 01:34:00.402
Grandpa!

1269
01:34:00.484 --> 01:34:03.203
Hey, come here to me.

1270
01:34:03.286 --> 01:34:05.322
You don't need to worry,
nobody's out there.

1271
01:34:05.404 --> 01:34:07.037
I've already checked.

1272
01:34:07.122 --> 01:34:09.064
Good, and there
probably never will be.

1273
01:34:09.149 --> 01:34:11.118
That's just how
my brain is wired.

1274
01:34:11.203 --> 01:34:12.310
I know.

1275
01:34:12.394 --> 01:34:13.578
I missed you.

1276
01:34:13.662 --> 01:34:15.233
- Hi, dad.
- Hey, sweetheart.

1277
01:34:15.314 --> 01:34:16.554
Everything okay?

1278
01:34:16.636 --> 01:34:18.345
Just never thought we'd
be in Witness Protection.

1279
01:34:18.430 --> 01:34:20.511
- Sorry about all that.
- It's alright. We're fine.

1280
01:34:20.595 --> 01:34:23.180
I'm just sorry about everything
that you've been through.

1281
01:34:23.264 --> 01:34:25.309
- Is everything okay with you?
- Couldn't be better.

1282
01:34:26.076 --> 01:34:28.947
- Anybody wanna go home?
- I do!

1283
01:34:29.029 --> 01:34:30.948
- I do!
- Me, too.

1284
01:34:32.613 --> 01:34:35.354
"Robinson was indicted
after admitting to the existence

1285
01:34:35.439 --> 01:34:37.091
of the morally
